[{\"slug\":\"airbrush-makeup-florida-brides\",\"title\":\"Why Airbrush Makeup Is a Game-Changer for Florida Brides\",\"date\":\"2026-03-07T15:49:03.156Z March 7, 2026\",\"category\":\"Bridal\",\"excerpt\":\"Discover why airbrush makeup is the top choice for Florida brides looking for long-lasting, heat-resistant coverage on their wedding day.\",\"content\":\"Florida's heat and humidity can be a bride's biggest beauty challenge, but airbrush makeup creates a breathable, sweat-resistant finish that lasts all day. The ultra-fine mist application bonds to skin seamlessly, offering flawless coverage that photographs beautifully in both indoor and outdoor settings. For Fort Lauderdale brides, airbrush application by a skilled artist like those at Velora Bella ensures your look stays fresh from the ceremony to the last dance.\"}]